  ('lead_lyk7kew', 'jenishjariwala', 'jenishjariwala2810@gmail.com', '8401043241', 'whop-course-buyer', 'new', NULL, 'He is right now doing a sales job and he is in sales because in the future he wants to start his own business and he has a tech background. He didn''t go through the free course because recently his mother has passed away. So he was busy with that and he sells solar plants. Average ticket size is around 1 crore and 20 thousand commission per sales and he feels that he loses one to two sales every single month because he doesn''t know how to do objection handling. However when I took the conversation in the point of mentorship and guidance, he said he is right now not in that mind frame to take up something new. Although he wants our help but not right now | Not Ready to Invest RN', 0, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-29T00:00:00.000Z', '[]'),
