  ('lead_dk8zsmf', 'pranavraut', 'pranavraut28@gmail.com', '9096564781', 'whop-course-buyer', 'new', NULL, 'Call booked for tomorrow 5 p.m. He was running his agency and was a partner but due to some internal issues he left. He is starting his own agency but right now he will be working as a freelancer. His average ticket size will be ₹12,000 to ₹30,000 with 70% profitability. He just started working on its services 15 days ago and he mentioned he wants:
